    Predict choices.

    predict_choices.Rd

    This function predicts the choices of decision makers.

    Usage

    predict_choices(x, data = NULL, overview = TRUE)

    Arguments

    x

    An object of class RprobitB_fit.

    data

    Either NULL or an object of class RprobitB_data.

    overview

    If TRUE, aggregate the prediction in a table.

    Value

    Either a table if overview = TRUE or a data frame otherwise.

    Examples

    data <- simulate_choices(form = choice ~ covariate, N = 10, T = 10, J = 2)
x <- mcmc(data)
